{"tid":1364750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次入元朗我地有樣野要攞盡","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T12:48:37.000Z","uid":279090,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"347069fb433042e15d481fec6e0ce225b5193eec","tid":1364750,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係光環呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry 我係P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出左反對通知書之後<br />\n我地就冇一條特定嘅路線行<br />\n本人其實最驚嘅係港共會成機揾人燒村 拆祠堂然後嫁禍比抗爭者<br />\n到時我地就會受人指責<br />\n場運動就少左好多人支持<br />\n。<br />\n所以我地今次要絕對和理優<br />\n唔係叫你有黑社會打你嘅時候<br />\n你唔打番7佢<br />\n而係盡量避免玩火同玩祠堂<br />\n傷到唔關事嘅人<br />\n如果有人放火 我地真係要救息左先<br />\n。<br />\n集中番反警黑合作<br />\n話比鄉黑知我地唔能驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"e44d7a08c81155082fed572ce65d0bbe236f3d40","tid":1364750,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e240175e6e9ac33449f3808114f5cb3314d272f6","tid":1364750,"uid":279090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"雖則話尊重前線決定<br />\n但真係好驚港共出陰招"},{"pid":"0de96702efed88d754150731b8329e55cf24e177","tid":1364750,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c358095c7c5d6bd24329c3e56a429b17b24c8656","tid":1364750,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"e39dcfd9eca730410e0369a491ed6ae08d834a7d","tid":1364750,"uid":27909